The package installs a complete LFS system plus openssl and wget.

The init system is either sysvinit, LFSInit, busybox or sysvinit for RPi denpending on what build script is used.

system-sysvinit-meta.LFSBuild
system-LFSInit-meta.LFSBuild
system-bbinit-meta.LFSBuild
system-pi-sysvinit-meta.LFSBuild
